  "keyFeatures": [
    "968+ production-ready agentic skills across 9 categories",
    "Universal SKILL.md format compatible with Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Cursor, Antigravity, and more",
    "Curated bundles organized by role (Web Wizard, Security Engineer, Full-Stack Developer, etc.)",
    "Step-by-step workflows for common development goals (Ship SaaS MVP, Security Audit, Build AI Agent)",
    "Interactive web app for browsing, searching, and copying skills with prompt builder",
    "Official skills from Anthropic, Vercel, Supabase, Microsoft, Google, and Apify",
    "NPX installer with automatic updates and multi-platform support",
